latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The registration process for UG courses commenced on 6th April 2022. Interested students can fill the CUET application form by visiting cuet.samarth.ac.in. 

CUET 2022 is scheduled to be conducted in the first and second week of July 2022. 

There is no weightage assigned to class 12th board marks in the admission process to the undergraduate courses at central universities including Delhi University from the 2022-23 academic session. 

Kindly note that the last date to register is 6th May 2022. 

Follow @communique_sscbs for further updates.

This Diwali, let's light the diyas of love and compassion that fill your life with happiness. May God send lots of light and joyousness towards you and your family. 

We, at Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies, wish you a safe and happy Diwali!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Azadi Ka Amrut Mahotsa
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
"If there is one place on the face of earth where all the dreams of living men have found a home from the very earliest days when man began the dream of existence, it is India!"

On the auspicious occasion of India's coming 75th Independence Day, we feel proud to celebrate "Azadi Ka Amrut Mahotsav." 

There is no greater feeling than singing the National Anthem with august pride and love for the country.
Join us to sing the National Anthem and celebrate the vividness, heritage, and tradition of the motherland of diversity. 

Jai Hind!

latestPosts.caption: The Hindu featured Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies (SSCBS), University of Delhi, for hosting a grand felicitation event honoring 34 of its notable alumni. The event celebrated alumni who have taken on leadership roles in top global organizations including McKinsey, PwC, L’Oréal, BCG, Deloitte, EY, and Accenture. During the event, Principal Prof. Poonam Verma unveiled a specially curated alumni diary showcasing the achievements and impact of these distinguished professionals. The coverage reflects SSCBS’s enduring legacy as a launchpad for global leadership and excellence.

latestPosts.caption:
Shaheed Sukhdev College Of Business Studies proudly presents Alumni Felicitation & Communion 2025, a heartfelt celebration of the inspiring journeys and achievements of our CBS alumni.
This year, we are thrilled to felicitate alumni who have been leading globally respected organizations and making a meaningful impact. Join us in welcoming:

1. Sanjeev Mittal, Batch of 1990 (CSO, Shubham Housing)
2. Arun Menon, Batch of 1991 (MD, Accenture)
3. Surender (Suren) Mehta, Batch of 1992 (CHRO, Nykaa)
4. Aseem Kaushik, Batch of 1994 (MD, L'Oréal India)

Scheduled for Sunday, April 13, 2025, at 11:00 AM at the Akash Ganga Auditorium, SSCBS, Rohini.

This much-anticipated event promises to be a vibrant celebration, bringing together alumni from across the years for a day of meaningful connections, cherished memories, and shared stories. The gathering will feature a networking lunch, engaging conversations, and captivating student performances — all set against the backdrop of fond nostalgia and enduring CBS spirit.

📌 Register now: https://lnkd.in/gSpaCKMH

Let’s make it a day to remember!

latestPosts.caption:
Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies is delighted to announce Alumni Felicitation & Communion 2025, an esteemed celebration dedicated to the ever-growing CBS alumni community.

The celebration will take place on April 13, 2025 (Sunday), from 11:00 AM onwards at the SSCBS Campus, Rohini, bringing together alumni from various batches to create a vibrant space for exchanging stories, experiences, and insights, with a networking lunch and performances.

Register using the link below: https://forms.gle/GPg8XJtif5tJgsjL8
We look forward to creating unforgettable memories together!

Every year, we proudly share the list of our best placement statistics and achievements with the world. 

This year, we are delighted to announce that all three Gold Medalists at IIM Ahmedabad for 2025 — Abhi Bansal (BBA(FIA) '21), Ishaan Jain (BBA(FIA) '22) and Aanchal Chadha (BMS '21) — are esteemed alumni of Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies (SSCBS), University of Delhi. 

Their outstanding accomplishments at one of the nation’s most prestigious institutions reflect their dedication, perseverance and the strong academic foundation instilled at SSCBS. 

We extend our heartfelt congratulations to our alumni on this remarkable achievement. Their success reinforces the legacy of excellence that our institution stands for.

For more inspiring achievements and success stories of our alumni, follow SCOBSA and witness how our community continues to shine.

Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies is delighted to announce Alumni Felicitation & Communion 2025, an esteemed celebration dedicated to the ever-growing CBS alumni community.

More than just an event, it is an opportunity to relive cherished memories and reconnect with those who have walked the same corridors. The celebration will take place on April 13, 2025 (Sunday), from 11:00 AM onwards at the SSCBS Campus, Rohini, bringing together alumni from various batches to create a vibrant space for exchanging stories, experiences, and insights, with a networking lunch and performances.

A special felicitation ceremony will honor our distinguished alumni who have achieved leadership positions such as CEO, CFO, COO, and other top executive roles at leading companies like BCG, Bain & Co., McKinsey, JP Morgan, and many more.

We warmly invite you to be part of this celebration and carry forward the legacy of our institution.

Register using the link below: https://forms.gle/GPg8XJtif5tJgsjL8
We look forward to creating unforgettable memories together!

latestPosts.caption:
आज शहीद सुखदेव कॉलेज ऑफ बिजनेस स्टडीज में आयोजित 5वें शहीद सुखदेव मेमोरियल लेक्चर 'शहीदों की विरासत, युवा शक्ति का प्रभाव—विकसित भारत का निर्माण' कार्यक्रम में सम्मिलित होकर छात्र-छात्राओं को संबोधित किया। 

भारत के स्वतंत्रता संग्राम में शहीद सुखदेव जी का योगदान अमूल्य था। उनका अदम्य साहस और राष्ट्रप्रेम आज भी देश के युवाओं के लिए प्रेरणा का स्रोत है।

आज भारत स्टार्टअप इकोसिस्टम और आत्मनिर्भर भारत अभियान के माध्यम से एक नई आर्थिक क्रांति का साक्षी बन रहा है। हमारे युवा बिजनेस और इनोवेशन के क्षेत्र में नए आयाम स्थापित कर रहे हैं। युवा शक्ति देश को आत्मनिर्भर और विकसित बनाने में अहम भूमिका निभा रहे है। युवा जब राष्ट्र निर्माण के संकल्प के साथ आगे बढ़ते हैं, तो देश नई ऊंचाइयों को छूता है।

@sscbsdu

Holi is more than just colors but it’s about togetherness, joy and new beginnings. 

Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies wishes you a Holi filled with happiness, harmony, and positivity. May it bring warmth, prosperity and cherished memories.

Wishing everyone a bright, beautiful and safe Holi!

At Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies, we honor the resilience, achievements, and contributions of women who shape our world. Today, we reaffirm our commitment to equality, empowerment, and a future where every woman thrives.

Here’s to the women who inspire, lead, and break barriers—today and always!

#IWD2025 #EmpowerHer #SSCBS #BreakingBarriers #WomenOfTomorrow

We, at Shaheed Sukhdev College of Business Studies, celebrate the sacred occasion of Maha Shivratri with devotion and joy. 

This day reminds us of the virtues of devotion, inner strength, and righteousness that guide our journey. As we come together to honor Lord Shiva, let us seek inspiration to stay strong, do good, and spread positivity. May the blessings of Lord Shiva inspire us to pursue excellence with unwavering determination and a spirit of humility.

May this special day bring peace, happiness, and success to everyone!
